   REQUEST FOR COMMENT ON PROPOSED AMENDMENTS TO THE FEDERAL RULES OF
   PRACTICE & PROCEDURE Comments due by February 15, 2002. The Judicial
   Conference's Advisory Committee on Bankruptcy Rules, Civil Rules,
   Criminal Rules, and Evidence Rules have proposed amendments to various
   rules and are seeking public comment on the proposed changes. The full
   text of the proposed rules and amendments and explanatory Committee
   Notes are stated in the Request for Comment pamphlets, which are posted
   on the Internet at rules>.
